      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUPEE MCGRAW (7) hit the ground running from out wide and on speed early but faded and swamped late when 6th at this track in Grade 5 company. Should be very hard to beat this time. GOLD CLASS COOL (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at The Meadows in a handy 30.33 beating In One Moment. Sure to be thereabouts. SCOUT ACE (5) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when third (30.14) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Expected to be in the finish again. MUGSHOT (4) will give backers a sight.",
